    <item>
      <title>贝莱德计划首次将共同基金转换为 ETF，时机成熟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/blackrock-plans-first-mutual-fund-to-etf-flip-in-sign-of-times</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司(BlackRock Inc.)本周制定了首次共同基金向ETF转换的计划，加入了越来越多的资产管理公司行列，这些资产管理公司在两种结构之间单向涌入的现金中实现了这一跃升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/blackrock-plans-first-mutual-fund-to-etf-flip-in-sign-of-times</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 19:33:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>借助热门通胀数据，财富管理机构为投资者带来了第二次机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/investment-opportunities-with-hot-inflation-higher-for-longer-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[不断上涨的价格和高利率令投资者感到沮丧。但顾问表示，顽固的价格增长为潜在利润丰厚的举措赢得了时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/investment-opportunities-with-hot-inflation-higher-for-longer-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 13:07:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>5% 的收益率让投资者再次发现值得为主动管理型债券基金付费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/bond-funds-dangling-5-yields-lure-cash-back-to-active-managers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[包括太平洋投资管理公司、贝莱德公司和资本集团在内的债券巨头都在悬挂5%的收益率前景，以说服投资者现在是时候将更多资产投入主动管理的固定收益基金了。客户正在关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/bond-funds-dangling-5-yields-lure-cash-back-to-active-managers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 10:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
